            <thetext>When opening a combobox whith a large number of entries in the popup where the popup entries are only reachable by scrolling/swiping up and down, you&#39;re not able to scroll/swipe without selecting an entry.

To reproduce open the widget browser:

    http://demo.qooxdoo.org/devel/widgetbrowser/index.html

In the &quot;Form&quot; tab tap on the popup button of the field labeled &quot;ComboBox&quot;. Try to swipe through the list entries. On swipe start the entry gets selected, but it should only be selected on a tap.

This is on iPad 3 with iOS 6.1.3.</thetext>
